OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772885577
OL,3,CWordsworth manuscript on tour in Asia
OL,4,Choping to inspire visitors to the Lakes
OL,6,FThe 'romantic' writer is famed for his
OL,7,Fdescriptions of his country's
OL,8,Flandscapes and it's hoped they can
OL,9,Fstill attract tourists 200 years after
OL,10,Fthey were written.
OL,12,FWilliam Wordsworth is best known for
OL,13,Fpoems such as "I Wandered Lonely as a
OL,14,FCloud" (Daffodils) and "The Prelude"
OL,15,Fboth inspired by and set in the Lake
OL,16,FDistrict.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
