PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772885577
OL,3,CWordsworth manuscript on tour in Asia
OL,4,Choping to inspire visitors to the Lakes
OL,6,FWordsworth Grasmere, which runs a
OL,7,Fmuseum dedicated to the poet, has
OL,8,Floaned "one of its most cherished
OL,9,Fmanuscripts" to museums in Asia,
OL,10,Fhoping it would inspire visitors to
OL,11,Fcome to the Lake District.
OL,13,FThe sonnet "On A Portrait Of The Duke
OL,14,FOf Wellington Upon The Field Of
OL,15,FWaterloo By Haydon" was written by
OL,16,FWordsworth in 1840 while he was
OL,17,Fclimbing Helvellyn - England's third
OL,18,Fhighest mountain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772885577
OL,3,CWordsworth manuscript on tour in Asia
OL,4,Choping to inspire visitors to the Lakes
OL,6,FAfter he sent a copy of it to his
OL,7,Ffriend Benjamin Robert Haydon, the
OL,8,Fartist painted a portrait of
OL,9,FWordsworth on the mountain, also on
OL,10,Fdisplay with the poem.
OL,12,FThe work has been on display at the
OL,13,FBusan Museum in South Korea and is due
OL,14,Fto go on display at Shanghai Museum
OL,15,FEast, in China, later this month.
OL,17,FMichael McGregor, from Wordsworth
OL,18,FGrasmere, said the countries were
OL,19,F"very important markets" for tourism.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
