OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772885577
OL,3,CWordsworth manuscript on tour in Asia
OL,4,Choping to inspire visitors to the Lakes
OL,6,F"As overseas visitors continue to
OL,7,Freturn to the UK, we need to ensure
OL,8,Fthat Cumbria, and in particular
OL,9,FGrasmere, is a destination they are
OL,10,Faware of," he said.
OL,12,FThe exhibition is part of a larger
OL,13,Fdisplay organised by the National
OL,14,FPortrait Gallery, bringing together
OL,15,Fsome of the most famous British
OL,16,Fwriters, including William
OL,17,FShakespeare, Jane Austen and J.R.R
OL,18,FTolkien.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
