FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772885577
OL,3,CWordsworth manuscript on tour in Asia
OL,4,Choping to inspire visitors to the Lakes
OL,6,FMcGregor added, "Our hope is that
OL,7,Fafter experiencing Wordsworth in the
OL,8,FBusan and Shanghai Museums, visitors
OL,9,Fwill one day come to Grasmere and Dove
OL,10,FCottage to continue their journey into
OL,11,Fthe poet's world."
OL,13,FWordsworth was born in Cockermouth in
OL,14,F1770 and moved to Dove Cottage in
OL,15,FGrasmere at the age of 29, where he
OL,16,Fwrote some of his most famous poems.
OL,18,FBoth homes are now museums.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
